<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣說起來，<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你請<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />幫忙蓋的房子，<delay8 />
聽說已經蓋好了呢？<delay20 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好棒喔～！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你願意的話，<delay8 />就讓我這位時尚女子<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />去幫你看看裝潢得怎麼樣吧？！<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼，<delay8 />不需要？<delay40 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不用跟我客氣啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />的家，<delay20 />
空間變得超大的對吧～？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定有可能<delay8 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是這座島上最大的耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這也是<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />拼命努力所獲得的成果吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我忍不住<delay8 />重新迷上你了唷～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你看過<delay8 />新的<colour id="1" />服務處<colour id="65535" />了嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那裡變得好時髦，讓我嚇了一跳！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那可是代表<tag a="110" b="33" />的門面，<delay20 />
對我們這些居民來說也很值得驕傲唷～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人沒事也想去那裡逛逛呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也知道我最喜歡購物了對吧？<delay40 />
所以<delay8 /><colour id="1" />Nook商店<colour id="65535" />變大以後，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真是超～開心的～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟店面越大，<delay8 />
逛起來也越開心嘛！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到能在本來是座無人島的這座島上，<delay8 />
享受這麼有意義的購物行程<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這真的要好好感謝<colour id="3" />豆狸<colour id="65535" />他們～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說<delay8 /><colour id="3" />傅達<colour id="65535" />的帳篷好像搭好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你已經和他見面聊過了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說他不只對生物很有研究，<delay20 />
還很了解化石呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想去找他說說話耶～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老實說，<delay8 />我完全沒想到
<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />居然會變得這麼壯觀，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我嚇了一大跳呢～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是仔細想想，<delay20 />
我們這座島上<delay8 />不是有很多稀有生物嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />地底下好像也埋有很多化石<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定就是因為蓋在這座島上<delay8 />才會這麼棒！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想<delay8 /><colour id="3" />傅達<colour id="65535" />心裡一定也很慶幸<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己能來這座島～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡開了間<colour id="1" />裁縫屋<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />我真是超～開心的～！！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟再怎麼說，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也是這座島上的時尚領袖對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前常～常在想<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
要是能有一間店開得近，<delay20 />
又能讓我慢慢挑選<delay8 />適合自己的衣服就好了～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然網路上什麼都買得到，<delay8 />
但尺寸之類的沒直接試穿過怎麼知道嘛！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘻嘻，<delay20 />所以我很常光顧那裡唷～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧有這條通往懸崖的道路，<delay20 />
只要我想<delay8 />從高處欣賞風景，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨時都可以去，超開心的！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />決定每天的散步路線<delay8 />
也就變得越來越有趣了～！<delay40 />
乾脆今天就去懸崖看看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個新搬來的居民<tag a="110" b="0" />嗯～<delay20 />
好像叫<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />對吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />選擇搬來<tag a="110" b="33" />，<delay8 />真聰明！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟再怎麼說，<delay8 />
這座島上有<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有我這個偶像一般的存在嘛。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />住在這裡<delay8 />一定每天都會遇到很多快樂的事～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想那個人也會很快就愛上這座島的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="1" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />博物館<colour id="65535" />重新開張後，<delay20 />不僅能看到
生物和化石，<delay8 />還能欣賞美術品呢。<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />你去過了嗎？
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣一來，<delay20 />想參觀<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />的遊客<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該會蜂擁而至吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不是該利用<tag a="110" b="33" />的<delay8 />
這股熱潮，<delay20 />偷偷為自己擬定一份<delay20 />
<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />提升知名度的作戰計畫呢？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
